    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Erasmus of Rotterdam (Brussels, 23 February
                    1534)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>Oláh hopes that Erasmus is well. He is surprised that he has not received
                            a letter from him for a long time, and he asks him to inform him about
                            his situation.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Nicolai Olai ad Desiderium Erasmum Roterodamum. </p>
                <p>Si bene tibi est valesque, ex animo laetor. Admiror plurimum me a
                    diuturno satis iam tempore nihil a te litterarum accepisse. Oro te, mi Erasme,
                    ut de statu ac incolumitate tua facias me certiorem, quem scito eum amicum et
                    nunc tibi esse et deinceps, dum vixero, futurum, quem tu sincerum, ut arbitror,
                    cognovisti. Laeta ac felicia omnia tibi perinde ac mihi cupio. Vale. </p>
                <p><placeName>Bruxellae</placeName> 23. Februarii 1534.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
